response.original_title: NJPW Presents CMLL Fantastica Mania 2017: Day 1
response.overview: On January 13, 2017, NJPW's Fantastica Mania 2017 tour kicked off at EDION Arena Osaka #2 in Osaka, Japan. The event was broadcast on Samurai! TV and featured a diverse card with wrestlers from both New Japan Pro-Wrestling (NJPW) and Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre (CMLL). The main event was a Six Man Tag Team Match pitting Hiroshi Tanahashi, Maximo Sexy, and Ryusuke Taguchi against CHAOS trio Kazuchika Okada, Will Ospreay, and Hechicero. Another notable match saw Los Ingobernables de Japon's EVIL and SANADA face off against Blue Panther Jr. and David Finlay in a tag team contest. Other wrestlers on the show include Atlantis, Mascara Dorada, Dragon Lee, Titan, and more!
response.title: NJPW Presents CMLL Fantastica Mania 2017: Day 1
